;Description
:This template is used to do insert married ship battle cards with link and description to articles.
;Syntax
:Type <code><nowiki>{{ShipMarriedBattleCard|<Ship name>|<Model>|align=<alignment>}}</nowiki></code> somewhere.
:Alternatively, <code><nowiki>{{ShipMarriedBattleCard|<Ship name>/<Model>|align=<alignment>}}</nowiki></code> also works.
;Sample outputs
:<code><nowiki>{{ShipMarriedBattleCard}}</nowiki></code> gives the default...{{ShipMarriedBattleCard}}
:<code><nowiki>{{ShipMarriedBattleCard|Ikazuchi}}</nowiki></code> gives...
:{{ShipMarriedBattleCard|Ikazuchi}}
:<code><nowiki>{{ShipMarriedBattleCard|Akatsuki/Kai Ni}}</nowiki></code> gives...
:{{ShipMarriedBattleCard|Akatsuki/Kai Ni}}
:<code><nowiki>{{ShipMarriedBattleCard|Standard Carrier Wo-Class|align=center}}</nowiki></code> gives...
:{{ShipMarriedBattleCard|Standard Carrier Wo-Class|align=center}}
:<code><nowiki>{{ShipMarriedBattleCard|Northern Princess|Final|align=right}}</nowiki></code> gives...
:{{ShipMarriedBattleCard|Northern Princess|Final|align=right}}
:<code><nowiki>{{ShipMarriedBattleCard|Ooyodo|align=center|Kai}}</nowiki></code> gives...
:{{ShipMarriedBattleCard|Ooyodo|align=center|Kai}}
;Limitation:
:The parameters can be in any order but <code><nowiki><Ship name></nowiki></code> must always be before <code><nowiki><Model></nowiki></code>
:The embedded link does not work in the ring area.